          question: 'In well-oxygenated cells, the TCA cycle is inhibited by high NADH/NAD⁺ ratios and ATP. How does this regulation relate to the concept of energy charge, and what would be the predicted effect on TCA cycle flux in a muscle cell immediately after intense exercise?',
